short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Change the timer sound of mobti.me.Icons made by Freepik from www.flaticon.com.Sounds provided by bigsoundbank.com

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: As remote software engineer and pairing/mobbing while coding becomes more prevalent, tools like mobti.me are emerging that help facilitate these pairing/mobbing sessions. This extension adds some extra timer sounds to mobti.me.
